sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Requester
    participant M as Manager
    participant P as Procurement
    participant V as Vendor
    participant F as Finance
    participant FD as Finance Director

    R->>M: Submit purchase request
    M-->>R: PR approved
    M->>P: Forward approved PR
    P->>V: Issue Purchase Order
    V-->>P: Order confirmation
    V->>F: Submit invoice
    F->>F: 3-way match verification

    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION — discrepancy handling
    rect rgba(186,117,23,0.15)
    Note over F,FD: ADDED — discrepancy handling path
        alt Match Successful
            F-->>V: Payment processed (NET30)
        else Match Failed
            F->>P: Notify discrepancy
            F->>FD: Escalate to Finance Director
            P->>V: Request corrected invoice
            V-->>F: Revised invoice submitted
            F->>F: Re-run 3-way match
            FD-->>F: Manual approval granted
            F-->>V: Payment processed after correction
        end
    end
    %% END CHANGED SECTION